# Code Review Rubric

This is the Cursor adapter for Hecate code-review guidance.

The canonical review rubric and output format live in
[`docs-ai/tasks/code-review.md`](../../docs-ai/tasks/code-review.md). Load the
relevant area skill as well, for example
[`docs-ai/skills/backend/SKILL.md`](../../docs-ai/skills/backend/SKILL.md) or
[`docs-ai/skills/ui/SKILL.md`](../../docs-ai/skills/ui/SKILL.md).

Do not keep a second review checklist in `.cursor`.
